modules.description: Provides functions to parse and manipulate the BUILD_PATH_PREFIX_MAP format, including converting between string representations and a map of prefix substitutions. Operates on strings and associative lists representing path mappings. Used to transform absolute paths in build logs and artifacts, ensuring consistent output across different build environments.

Encodes and decodes path prefixes, pairs, and maps into strings, with error handling for invalid inputs. Rewrites paths by replacing known prefixes with their corresponding targets from the map. Processes structured data like path mappings and ensures safe transformation of file or URL paths.
